data.description: Charming single story home nestled in a quiet and clean culdesac. Front home features fresh landscaped yard with sprinkler system, seller just replaced A//C unit, spacious drive way, concrete back fencing, backyard patio to entertain guest, shed, pool & spa for your comfort. Easy access to Hwy 99, minutes away from Stockton Metropolitan Airport, walking distance from Ernie Shropshire Park. Inspection Report is attached and all repairs have been completed. This home is a must see!
